<div class="mv">
  <div class="mv__slider">
    <div class="slide">
      <img class="-hidden-sp" src="<%= conf.assets.image %>/mv_img1_pc.jpg" alt="" />
      <img class="-hidden-pc" src="<%= conf.assets.image %>/mv_img1_sp.jpg" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="slide">
      <img class="-hidden-sp" src="<%= conf.assets.image %>/mv_img2_pc.jpg" alt="" />
      <img class="-hidden-pc" src="<%= conf.assets.image %>/mv_img2_sp.jpg" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="slide">
      <img class="-hidden-sp" src="<%= conf.assets.image %>/mv_img3_pc.jpg" alt="" />
      <img class="-hidden-pc" src="<%= conf.assets.image %>/mv_img3_sp.jpg" alt="" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="layout">
    <div class="copy">
      <div class="copy_wrapper">
        <div class="copy_wrapper--top">
          <div class="copy_animation">
            <span>F</span><span>i</span><span>l</span><span>e</span><span>M</span><span>a</span><span>k</span
            ><span>e</span><span>r</span>
          </div>
          <div class="copy_symbol copy_symbol--1"><img src="<%= conf.assets.image %>/multiplicative.png" alt="" /></div>
          <div class="copy_animation">
            <span>ア</span><span>ジ</span><span>ャ</span><span>イ</span><span>ル</span><span>開</span><span>発</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="copy_wrapper--bottom">
          <div class="copy_symbol copy_symbol--2"><img src="<%= conf.assets.image %>/equal.png" alt="" /></div>
          <div class="copy_animation"><span>D</span><span>X</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="mv__text">
      日々進化し変化する市場に合わせた、<br />
      スピーディかつ柔軟なシステム開発でDXを実現し、<br />
      NEXTSTAGEへの扉を開く。
    </p>

    <div class="scrolldown">
      Scroll
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="loop_wrapper">
    <div>Freeandopen Inc.</div>
    <div>Freeandopen Inc.</div>
    <div>Freeandopen Inc.</div>
    <div>Freeandopen Inc.</div>
    <div>Freeandopen Inc.</div>
    <div>Freeandopen Inc.</div>
    <div>Freeandopen Inc.</div>
  </div>
</div>